Where does this test live?

```php
// A test that stores a photo:
$user = User::factory()->create();

$this->actingAs($user)
     ->post('/photos', [
         'title' => 'Sunset',
         'url'   => 'https://example.com/sunset.jpg',
     ])
     ->assertRedirect('/photos');

$this->assertDatabaseHas('photos', ['title' => 'Sunset']);
```

